function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	idMarker = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "marker")[1]
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, idMarker, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idFollower, 1.0)
	end
end

	SetTraversalEnabled(idTraversal, false)
	
	Hydra.EventSend("BrolWalk")
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	--Play Boss Victory Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride("CSD_Step_MtCivo_TempleoftheTriune", "Music_Boss_TyrantKing_Victory")
	------------------------------------------------------
	-- First Time Rewards
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Brol", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Brol")
	end
	
	------------------------------------------------------
end
